Rakshit Singh went to Kisan Mahapanchayat in Meerut today and resigned from his job in support of farmers. He says the channels aren't allowing to show the truth and therefore "laat maarta hu aisi naukri ko" ..Success is not final, failure is not fatal: it is the courage to continue that counts...Bravo Rakshit Singh

A Happy New Year! Best wishes for a happy, and more importantly, healthy and wealthy new year. Whether online or in-person, looking forward to being in touch next year!

A rough translation of Iqbal’s famous poem ‘Adam Is Received By The Spirit Of The Earth’ may boost us all to welcome the New Year with animated spirit.

Open your eyes and look above,
Look at the streak of dawn;
Look at the veiling of the vision;
Look at the banishment unfair;
Look at the battle of hope and fear.
Yours are the clouds, the rains, the skies,
Yours are the winds, the storms,
The spark in you is a radiant sun;
A new world lives in you;
You guard eternal secrets divine,
And live a life of obedient power;
Look at the world as shaped by your will.

A very Happy New Year to you again. May 2021 give us all professional satisfaction and make achieving our goals easier.

